sellerCard.description: I'm Abdul Rahman, a skilled full-stack Software Engineer,Django,Mern web & App developer with a software engineering background. I excel in creating custom web and mobile solutions. I have experience in programming languages such as Python, C++, Java, and JavaScript,Dart. With my expertise in front-end and back-end development, I can deliver responsive and dynamic web & Apps that provide an exceptional user experience. If you need a new website or want to revamp an existing one, I can provide end-to-end solutions tailored to your business needs. Contact me to discuss your project requirements.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What is full stack website development?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Full stack website development involves both frontend development and backend development to create a complete website.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Why should I hire a full stack developer for my website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: A full stack developer can handle both the frontend and backend, ensuring seamless integration and functionality of your website.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What is the difference between a frontend developer and a backend developer?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: A frontend developer focuses on the user interface and experience, while a backend developer handles server-side logic, databases, and APIs.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What do your website development packages include?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: My packages include varying levels of frontend and backend development, UI/UX design, responsive design, API integration, and database setup.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you develop RESTFul APIs?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes i can help you with that.

questionsAndAnswers.question: can you full stack web development in mern stack?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes for sure. I can develop full stack web application using mern stack.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you develop mobile application and web application together
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Sure, I can develop web and mobile applications together with a single code base using flutter or react-native.
